Welcome to Lone Star Loaners! 

We are a car-sharing host with over 5 years of car-sharing experience and over 5,000 trips on the Turo platform. Our fleet is managed by the husband and wife team, Aubrey and HP, and we currently have 20 cars available to rent on Turo, but our fleet is growing monthly.

If you are looking for a reliable host, then look no further - we manage our Turo fleet full-time and our reviews speak for themselves. Aubrey manages all guest communication and is available nearly 24/7 to assist with guest questions, concerns, or any issues that may arise. While HP manages the vehicles, cleans the cars between bookings, and ensures that our fleet is always properly maintained.

All of our cars have instant booking turned on, and all of them are remote key exchanges - meaning we won't actually be there when you pick up the vehicle. This gives you a more convenient and flexible booking and rental experience. 

Our cars aren't perfect, they all have wear and tear, so if you are looking for a perfect rental car that is of showroom quality then, unfortunately, our cars are not for you. But, if you are looking for a professionally maintained, reliable, clean car at an affordable price, then our fleet is perfect for you.

Though all of our cars have wear and tear they are all meticulously maintained, they are all cleaned and disinfected between every single rental and they will all get you to where you need to go at an affordable price. 

Our Turo profile speaks for itself, if you are looking for a host you can count on then look no further than Lone Star Loaners.

We look forward to hosting you!

- Aubrey & HP
